subject_information.comments: Really made me wonder what things look like to the director.
subject_information.strategy: Most of the time is was very straightforward - just do exactly as I was told. A couple times things were ambiguous, so I had to weigh what he or she might have actually meant.  One time I was told to move the "bottom block" and saw only one block. But direction to move made it obvious that's the only one that could be moved.
